        The Event Gathering Our Voices National Aboriginal Youth Conference takes place in
        a different community each year. In 2016,the conference will be hosted at the
        Victoria conference Centre in Victoria, BC. Over the course of four days we will
        gather over 1,500 delegates together from across Canada to conduct ceremonies,
        host 50+ workshops and offer exciting ways to engage, inform, educate and
        entertain the youth.
    </p>

